OL,3,COne in five pro footballers using snus
OL,4,Cor nicotine pouches, survey finds
OL,6,FAround one in five male and female
OL,7,Fprofessional players who took part in
OL,8,Fa new survey are currently using snus,
OL,9,Fnicotine pouches or both.
OL,11,FThe study by Loughborough University,
OL,12,Fcommissioned by the Professional
OL,13,FFootballers' Association (PFA), also
OL,14,Fidentified that two out of five had
OL,15,Ftried the pouches at least once in the
OL,16,Fpast.
OL,18,FSnus contains tobacco and is not
OL,19,Flegally available to buy in the UK.
