OL,3,COne in five pro footballers using snus
OL,4,Cor nicotine pouches, survey finds
OL,6,FTobacco-free nicotine pouches are
OL,7,Flegal to buy, and were found to be
OL,8,Fmore commonly used among players. The
OL,9,Fpouches are usually placed between the
OL,10,Fupper lip and the gums.
OL,12,FThe report states the true figures are
OL,13,F"likely" to be even higher due to
OL,14,Fplayers not wanting to disclose use,
OL,15,Feven in an anonymous survey.
OL,17,FAround 18% of the 628 male players
OL,18,Fsurveyed, based at either Premier
OL,19,FLeague or EFL clubs, said they
OL,20,Fcurrently used it.
