OL,3,COne in five pro footballers using snus
OL,4,Cor nicotine pouches, survey finds
OL,6,FOf the 51 Women's Super League players
OL,7,Fsurveyed, 22% said used snus.
OL,9,FParticipants said improved mental
OL,10,Freadiness was a key benefit of the
OL,11,Fsubstance, with 41% of male players
OL,12,Fsaying they used it to help relax,
OL,13,Fmost commonly after training and after
OL,14,Fmatches. That figure was 64% among
OL,15,Ffemale players.
OL,17,FOne of the 16 professional club
OL,18,Fperformance and medical staff members
OL,19,Falso interviewed for the report said
OL,20,Fplayers used it as a "coping
OL,21,Fmechanism".
