OL,3,COne in five pro footballers using snus
OL,4,Cor nicotine pouches, survey finds
OL,6,FThe pouches are also used as an
OL,7,Fappetite suppressant, the report found.
OL,9,FHowever, the report also highlighted
OL,10,Fthe potential negative physical
OL,11,Fimpacts.
OL,13,FEvidence suggests snus is associated
OL,14,Fwith an increased risk of oesophagus
OL,15,Fand pancreatic cancer in comparison to
OL,16,Fnon-smokers, and to an increased risk
OL,17,Fof cardiovascular disease.
OL,19,FThere is strong evidence of an
OL,20,Fassociation between snus use and mouth
OL,21,Flesions.
