OL,3,COne in five pro footballers using snus
OL,4,Cor nicotine pouches, survey finds
OL,6,FThe survey found users often started
OL,7,Fusing the products in a bid to fit in
OL,8,Fwith other, often more senior, team-
OL,9,Fmates. For male players 56% gave this
OL,10,Fas a reason, rising to 73% among women.
OL,12,FOne surveyed player admitted: "I have
OL,13,Fquit twice for eight months but always
OL,14,Fseem to start doing it again. I find
OL,15,Fit hard to quit when I'm around it all
OL,16,Fday."
