OL,3,COne in five pro footballers using snus
OL,4,Cor nicotine pouches, survey finds
OL,6,FA staff member at a club said they had
OL,7,Fcome across a player whose career had
OL,8,Fmainly been spent in the Premier
OL,9,FLeague and Championship who described
OL,10,Fthemselves as a "heavy user".
OL,12,FThey told the staff member: "I'd love
OL,13,Fto come off it, but I can't. It's just
OL,14,Feverywhere I look. Every other
OL,15,Fplayer's taking it, I go to fill my
OL,16,Fcar up and it's at the pump stands.
OL,17,FIt's just too easy."
OL,19,FApproximately half the current users
OL,20,Fin the men's game said they wanted to
OL,21,Fquit within the next 12 months.
