OL,3,COne in five pro footballers using snus
OL,4,Cor nicotine pouches, survey finds
OL,6,FUsers also reported suffering from
OL,7,Fnicotine dependence, such as using it
OL,8,Fwithout awareness or intention.
OL,10,FShort-term withdrawal symptoms were
OL,11,Falso common ` cravings, irritability,
OL,12,Frestlessness and anxiety.
OL,14,FThe report found club bans had not
OL,15,Fbeen effective in deterring use, and
OL,16,Frecommended personalised, external
OL,17,Fsupport and to avoid stigmatising
OL,18,Fthose seeking help.
